Faq.title: How can I order?

Faq.description: We have 99RS minimum order value and you can order for min 99RS amount.
Faq.title: Is there a minimum order value?

Faq.description: Delivery fee varies from city to city and is applicable if order value is below a certain amount. Additionally, certain restaurants might have fixed delivery fees. Delivery fee (if any) is specified on the 'Review Order' page.
Faq.title: Do you charge for delivery?

Faq.description: Standard delivery times vary by the location selected and prevailing conditions. Once you select your location, an estimated delivery time is mentioned for each restaurant.
Faq.title: How long do you take to deliver?

Faq.description: We will deliver from any restaurant listed on the search results for your location. We recommend enabling your GPS location finder and letting the app auto-detect your location.
Faq.title: Can I order from any location?
